behavior prepare_scramble_eggs(fryingpan:item, oil:item, food_egg:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inhand(food_egg)
        observe(fryingpan, "Is there oil inside it")
        achieve clean(oil)
        achieve close_char(char, fryingpan)
        achieve inside(food_egg, fryingpan)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind stove: item where:
            is_stove(stove)
        bind fryingpan: item where:
            is_fryingpan(fryingpan)
        bind food_egg: item where:
            is_food_egg(food_egg)
        bind oil: item where:
            is_oil(oil)

        if not close(fryingpan, stove):
            move_fryingpan_close_to_stove(fryingpan, stove)
        
        if not inside_char(char, fryingpan):
            achieve close_char(char, fryingpan)

        prepare_scramble_eggs(fryingpan, oil, food_egg)

def is_fryingpan_clean_for_use(fryingpan: item):

    symbol is_clean_for_use=dirty(fryingpan)
    return is_clean_for_use

        achieve inside(oil, fryingpan) # Place oil in the frying pan

behavior crack_egg_into_fryingpan(food_egg: item, fryingpan: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(food_egg, fryingpan) # Crack the egg into the frying pan

behavior scramble_eggs(egg:item, fryingpan:item, stove:item):

        # Place the egg in the frying pan
